        <detaileddescription>
<para>Render the <ref refid="namespaceMR_1_1UI" kindref="compound">UI</ref>. This is repeated for each viewport. Here you can either render immediately, or insert a task into <computeroutput>params.tasks</computeroutput>, which get Z-sorted.<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>params</computeroutput> will remain alive as long as the tasks are used.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>You&apos;ll have at most one living task at a time, so you can write a non-owning pointer to an internal task. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
